transcripts.text: You know, sexual abuse assault allegations are dime a dozen in politics, especially these days.  They come from all sides.  It is not a surprise that somebody on the left...

But there is a significant difference between this one and Christine Blasey Ford's allegation against Brett Kavanaugh, and that... Yeah, Tara Reid did tell people at the time, and that is a very significant difference.  My attitude towards it is, yes, I 100% support due process, except I do make an exception for Joe Biden.  With Joe Biden, I say he should go directly to jail.  Straight to jail.
